ctions et leur impact avec le plus grand nombre, gr\u00e2ce aux marques partenaires, aux \u00e9quipes de la Fondation des Femmes, \u00e0 la Cit\u00e9 Audacieuse et \u00e0 nos formidables b\u00e9n\u00e9voles. MERCI \ud83d\ude42\u00a0\u00bb<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-642cf68 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"642cf68\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-47d8378 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"47d8378\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"789\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Alexane-referente-pole-collecte-789x1024.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-45614\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Alexane-referente-pole-collecte-789x1024.jpg 789w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Alexane-referente-pole-collecte-231x300.jpg 231w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Alexane-referente-pole-collecte-768x996.jpg 768w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Alexane-referente-pole-collecte.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 789px) 100vw, 789px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c3f4b93 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c3f4b93\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c4d4448 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c4d4448\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Alexane<\/p>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t